  "description": "I\u0026rsquo;m thinking about my Fediverse profile as where I perform as a sort of, well, social justice warrior, but specifically, I see myself often succeeding when I try and \u0026ldquo;beat the drum\u0026rdquo; of validating anger and rage. And my Substack is often where I\u0026rsquo;m analyzing my melancholy as a mechanism of hoping.\nSo, this relates to my brand and my public image.\nAnd that got me wondering what persons of the Catholic Church relate to those practices. Here\u0026rsquo;s my keyword salad.\n",
